data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104zos1665702822168_2.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zos1665702822168_2.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zos1665702822168_2.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"zos1665702822168\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Allow Carriage Return\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Allow carriage return in this field. Applicable only to Unifields.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zos1665702822168__section_w2855ab1b5b1_w2856ab1b5_w2857ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"zos1665702822168__table_d11450e1_d11451e1_d11452e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"zos1665702822168__table_d11450e1_d11451e1_d11452e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"zos1665702822168__table_d11450e1_d11451e1_d11452e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zos1665702822168__table_d11450e1_d11451e1_d11452e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">Undefined</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zos1665702822168__table_d11450e1_d11451e1_d11452e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Equivalent to <code class=\"ph codeph\">YCR</code>. </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zos1665702822168__table_d11450e1_d11451e1_d11452e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zos1665702822168__table_d11450e1_d11451e1_d11452e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Sets the <code class=\"ph codeph\">YCR</code> field syntax code, which allows carriage\n                           returns.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zos1665702822168__table_d11450e1_d11451e1_d11452e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"zos1665702822168__table_d11450e1_d11451e1_d11452e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Sets the <code class=\"ph codeph\">NCR</code> field syntax code, which does not allow\n                           carriage returns.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zos1665702822168__section_jcc_lqq_qwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1105758e148\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zos1665702822168__p_d99089e1_d99090e1_d99091e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zlt1665702557043.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zlt1665702557043.html\" title=\"The Field Syntax property specifies the input format for data, including the entry format (for example, 1-Dec-14 or 20141201), the allowed characters, and whether the field is mandatory or read-only.\">Field Syntax</a>\n</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8424476\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8424476\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" ro